title: Speed Dial
content:
Hello,

you have disabled the Speed Dial add-ons without any further information, plus you didn't add or do some way to restore the saved tabs in this add-ons!!!! 

I have many important website added there and now i cannot recall the name!!!!

i need to know what is the way to have what was my saved website?
creator: bushnaq.ag
